(13, 'HTML Colors', '<h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>HTML&nbsp;<span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Colors</span></b></h1><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><p class=\"intro\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">HTML colors are specified using predefined color names, or RGB, HEX, HSL, RGBA, HSLA values.</p><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>Color Names</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">In HTML, a color can be specified by using a color name:</p><div class=\"w3-row w3-center\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin: 0px -16px; line-height: 80px; color: white; text-align: center !important;\"><div class=\"w3-col l3 m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 270.663px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: tomato;\">Tomato</div></div><div class=\"w3-col l3 m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 270.663px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: orange;\">Orange</div></div><div class=\"w3-col l3 m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 270.663px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: dodgerblue;\">DodgerBlue</div></div><div class=\"w3-col l3 m6 w3-padding\" s