ing: inherit; color: red;\">color<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">:</span>&nbsp;red<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">;</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">}</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/style<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/head<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>body<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>h1<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>This is a heading<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/h1<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>p<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>This is a paragraph.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/p<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-si