"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;href<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"#C4\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>Jump to Chapter 4<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Or, add a link to the bookmark (\"Jump to Chapter 4\"), from another page:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;href<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"html_demo.html#C4\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>Jump to Chapter 4<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>External Paths</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">External pages can be referenced with a full URL or with a path relative to the current web page.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">This example uses a full URL to link to a web page:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;href<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"https://www.w3schools.com/html/default.asp\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>HTML tutorial<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">This example links to a page located in the html folder on the current web site:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;href<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"/html/default.asp\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>HTML tutorial<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">This example links to a page located in the same folder as the current page:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;href<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"default.asp\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>HTML tutorial<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><div class=\"w3-panel w3-note\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0.01em 16px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 204); border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 235, 59);\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">You can read more about file paths in the chapter&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/html/html_filepaths.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">HTML File Paths</a>.</p></div><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Chapter Summary</h2><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Use the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">&lt;a&gt;</code>&nbsp;element to define a link</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Use the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">href</code>&nbsp;attribute to define the link address</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Use the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">target</code>&nbsp;attribute to define where to open the linked document</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Use the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">&lt;img&gt;</code>&nbsp;element (inside &lt;a&gt;) to use an image as a link</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Use the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">id</code>&nbsp;attribute (id=\"<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">value</em>\") to define bookmarks in a page</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Use the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">href</code>&nbsp;attribute (href=\"#<em style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">value</em>\") to link to the bookmark</li></ul><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">HTML Link Tags</h2><table class=\"w3-table-all notranslate\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; width: 1050.4px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); margin: 20px 0px;\"><tbody style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top; width: 314.4px;\">Tag</th><th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Description</th></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_a.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">&lt;a&gt;</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Defines a hyperlink</td></tr></tbody></table></div>', 1, 1, 0, '2018-03-31 14:04:53', '2018-04-02 16:06:16');
INSERT INTO `tblsection` (`SectionID`, `SectionName`, `SectionContent`, `ChapterID`, `AddedByAdminID`, `SectionStatus`, `CreatedDateTime`, `UpdatedDateTime`) VALUES
(16, 'HTML Images', '<div class=\"w3-col l10 m12\" id=\"main\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 1082.66px; transition: margin-left 0.4s; padding: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px;\"><b>HTML&nbsp;<span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Images</span></b></h1><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><p class=\"intro\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 16px;\">Images can improve the design and the appearance of a web page.</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>img<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;src<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"img_girl.jpg\"</span>&nbsp;alt<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"Girl in a jacket\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>img<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;src<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"img_chania.jpg\"</span>&nbsp;alt<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"Flowers in Chania\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>HTML Images Syntax</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">In HTML, images are defined with the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">&lt;img&gt;</code>&nbsp;tag.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">&lt;img&gt;</code>&nbsp;tag&nbsp;is empty, it contains attributes only, and does not have a closing tag.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">src</code>&nbsp;attribute specifies the URL (web address) of the image:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>img<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;src<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">url</i>\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>The alt Attribute</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">alt</code>&nbsp;attribute provides an alternate text for an image, if the user for some reason cannot view it (because of slow connection, an error in the src attribute, or if the user uses a screen reader).</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The value of the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">alt</code>&nbsp;attribute should describe the image:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>img<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;src<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"img_chania.jpg\"</span>&nbsp;alt<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"Flowers in Chania\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">If a browser cannot find an image, it will display the value of the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">alt</code>&nbsp;attribute:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>img<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;src<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"wrongname.gif\"</span>&nbsp;alt<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"Flowers in Chania\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><div class=\"w3-panel w3-note\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0.01em 16px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 204); border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 235, 59);\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Note:</strong>&nbsp;The&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">alt</code>&nbsp;attribute is required. A web page will not validate correctly without it.</p></div><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>Image Size - Width and Height</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">You can use the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">style</code>&nbsp;attribute to specify the width and height of an image.</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: 