 inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_tbody.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">&lt;tbody&gt;</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Groups the body content in a table</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_tfoot.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">&lt;tfoot&gt;</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Groups the footer content in a table</td></tr></tbody></table></div>', 1, 1, 0, '2018-03-31 14:04:53', '2018-04-02 16:16:32');
