(20, 'HTML Classes', '<div class=\"w3-col l10 m12\" id=\"main\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 1082.66px; transition: margin-left 0.4s; padding: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px;\"><b>HTML&nbsp;<span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The class Attribute</span></b></h1><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>Using The class Attribute</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">class</code>&nbsp;attribute specifies one or more class names for an HTML element.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The class name can be used by CSS and JavaScript to perform certain tasks for elements with the specified class name.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">In CSS, to select elements with a specific class, write a period (.) character, followed by the name of the class:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Use CSS to style all elements with the class name \"city\":</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>style<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">.city</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">{</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;background-color<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">:</span>&nbsp;tomato<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; color<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">:</span>&nbsp;white<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; padding<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">:</span>&nbsp;10px<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\">}</span>&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/style<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>h2<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\