0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>Bookmarks with ID and Links</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">HTML bookmarks are used to allow readers to jump to specific parts of a Web page.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bookmarks can be useful if your webpage is very long.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">To make a bookmark, you must first create the bookmark, and then add a link to it.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">When the link is clicked, the page will scroll to the location with the bookmark.</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>Example</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">First, create a bookmark with the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">id</code>&nbsp;attribute:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>h2<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;id<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"C4\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>Chapter 4<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/h2<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Then, add a link to the bookmark (\"Jump to Chapter 4\"), from within the same page:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;href<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"#C4\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>Jump to Chapter 4<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Or, add a link to the bookmark (\"Jump to Chapter 4\"), from another page:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">&nbsp;href<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">=\"html_demo.html#C4\"</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>Jump to Chapter 4<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/a<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div></div>', 1, 1, 0, '2018-03-31 14:04:53', '2018-04-02 16:34:51');
