herit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/p<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/SECTION<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Good:</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>section<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>p<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span>This is a paragraph.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/p<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/section<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: med