=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">clearWatch()</code>&nbsp;- Stops the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">watchPosition()</code>&nbsp;method.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The example below shows the&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16.5px; color: crimson; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\">watchPosition()</code>&nbsp;method. You need an accurate GPS device to test this (like iPhone):</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><div class=\"w3-code notranslate htmlHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;; font-size: 16px; width: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(76, 175, 80); word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>script<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">var</span>&nbsp;x = document.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">getElementById</span>(<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"demo\"</span>);<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">function</span>&nbsp;getLocation() {<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">if</span>&nbsp;(navigator.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">geolocation</span>) {<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; navigator.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">geolocation</span>.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">watchPosition</span>(showPosition);<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">else</span>&nbsp;{<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; x.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">innerHTML</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"Geolocation is not supported by this browser.\"</span>;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">}<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">function</span>&nbsp;showPosition(position) {<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; x.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">innerHTML</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"Latitude: \"</span>&nbsp;+ position.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">coords</span>.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">latitude</span>&nbsp;+&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"&lt;br&gt;Longitude: \"</span>&nbsp;+ position.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">coords</span>.<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">longitude</span>;&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span>}<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&lt;</span>/script<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">&gt;</span></span></div></div></div>', 5, 1, 0, '2018-03-31 14:18:00', '2018-04-02 19:50:57'),
(49, 'HTML Drag/Drop', '<div class=\"w3-col l10 m12\" id=\"main\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 1082.66px; transition: margin-left 0.4s; padding: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px;\"><b>HTML5&nbsp;<span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Drag and Drop</span></b></h1><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>Drag and Drop</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Drag and drop is a very common feature. It is when you \"grab\" an object and drag it to a different location.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">In HTML5, drag and drop is part of the standard: Any element can be draggable.</p><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>Browser Support</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The numbers in the table specify the first browser version that fully supports Drag and Drop.</p><table class=\"browserref notranslate\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; width: 1050.4px;\"><tbody style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: 32px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); font-weight: normal; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); padding: 11px 5px 11px 16px; vertical-align: middle; width: 210.4px; font-size: 16px;\">API</th><th class=\"bsChrome\" title=\"Chrome\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: 32px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); font-wei