r><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top; height: 25px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bookmarks</strong></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top; height: 25px;\"></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top; height: 25px;\"></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Open the bookmarks menu</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Ctrl + B</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Cmd + B</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Add bookmark for current page</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Ctrl + D</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Cmd + Opt + B or Cmd + Shift + B</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Open browsing history</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Ctrl + H</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Cmd + Shift + H or Cmd + Y