(81, 'CSS Colors', '<div class=\"w3-col l10 m12\" id=\"main\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 940.828px; transition: margin-left 0.4s; padding: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px;\"><b>CSS&nbsp;<span class=\"color_h1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Colors</span></b></h1><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><p class=\"intro\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 16px;\">Colors are specified using predefined color names, or RGB, HEX, HSL, RGBA, HSLA values.</p><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><b>Color Names</b></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">In HTML, a color can be specified by using a color name:</p><div class=\"w3-row w3-center\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; text-align: center !important; margin: 0px -16px; line-height: 80px; color: white;\"><div class=\"w3-col l3 m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 235.203px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: tomato;\">Tomato</div></div><div class=\"w3-col l3 m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 235.203px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: orange;\">Orange</div></div><div class=\"w3-col l3 m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 235.203px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: dodgerblue;\">DodgerBlue</div></div><div class=\"w3-col l3 m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 235.203px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: mediums