iv><div class=\"w3-col m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 422.406px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">hsl(0, 100%, 25%)</div></div><div class=\"w3-col m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 422.406px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">hsl(0, 100%, 50%)</div></div><div class=\"w3-col m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 422.406px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 128, 128);\">hsl(0, 100%, 75%)</div></div><div class=\"w3-col m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 422.406px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 204, 204); color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">hsl(0, 100%, 90%)</div></div><div class=\"w3-col m6 w3-padding\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 422.406px; padding: 8px 16px !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">hsl(0, 100%, 100%)</div></div></div></div></div><hr style=\"height: 0px; overflow: visible; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Shades of gray are often defined by setting the hue and saturation to 0, and adjust the lightness from 0% to 100% to get darker/lighter shades:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(241, 241, 241); padding: 0.01em 16px; margin: 20px 0px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16) 0px 2px 4px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0px 2px 10px 0px !i